ov-Smirnov tests suggest that field BHB stars and BHB stars in globular\nclusters share a common distribution of luminosities, with the exception of\nglobular clusters with extended BHBs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 May 2005 19:57:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 May 2005 20:29:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
