nce of wind asphericity that we\nfind in LBVs with strong H$\\alpha$ emission and recent (last $\\sim$ 10 years)\nstrong variability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 May 2005 12:22:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
